quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Dũni yikr pẽnegame tɩ kiuugã pãrge(Nɑbiyɑɑmã wɑkɑtẽ wã) tɩ rẽndɑ yɑɑ yelsolemde n kõ nɑbiyɑɑmã pʋʋsg lɑ tɩlgr be ɑ yĩngɑ."
  54,2,"La b sã n yã yel-soalmã b balldame la b yetẽ: ""yaa tɩɩm sẽn duumdi""."
  54,3,"Tɩ b yags la b pʋg b yamleoodo, la yell fãa tara tεka."
  54,4,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, kibay waa bãmb nengẽ, pεlen-yɩk sẽn be a pʋgẽ."
  54,5,"Bãng-nafa sẽn ta tεka, la bugsg pa nafd ye."
  54,6,"Bɩ f gõd kuidg n bas-ba. Raar ning boaandã sẽn boond n tʋgd yell kɑseng sẽn zɩ n yã."
  54,7,"B ninã yaa sẽn nodg n yit yaadẽ wã, tɩ bãmb yaa wala sʋy sẽn yelge."
  54,8,"N rondgd n rabd boaandẽ wã. Kɩfr-dãmb yetame: ""yãoã yaa keelem raare"""
  54,9,"A Nuuh nebã ra yagsa bãmb taoore, n yags Tõnd yambã la b yeel tɩ yaa gãeenga, la b yɩk a pεlenga."
  54,10,"T'a bool a Soabã: ad mam yaa b sẽn wil-a soaba, bɩ F sõnge."
  54,11,"Tɩ Tõnd pak saag rag-noyã tɩ yaa koom sẽn kiigdi."
  54,12,"La d pãrg Tẽngã t'a yaa ko-ninim tɩ koomã yek taab yell zug sẽn da korde."
  54,13,"La D rɩk-a ra-pɛgd la bay zugu (koglgo.)"
  54,14,"T'a zoetẽ, Tõnd nenem pʋgẽ tɩ yaa rolbo, n nɑ n sõng ned ninga b sẽn kɩɩs-a (A Nuuh)."
  54,15,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd bas-a lame t'a yaa yel-soalma, la rẽ yĩnga tẽegd beeme bɩ?"
  54,16,"La Mam naongã ne M bugsgã yɩɩ wãn-wãna?"
  54,17,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd yolsa Alkʋrãanã tẽegr yĩnga, la tẽegd beeme bɩ?"
  54,18,"A Aad rãmb yagsame, la Mam naonga ne M bugsgã yɩɩ wãn-wãna?"
  54,19,"Tõnd tʋmsa seb-kεgeng b zug ra-toog raar sẽn duumdi."
  54,20,"A lugsda neba, tɩ b yaa wala tamar-tɩɩs yẽg sẽn võoge."
  54,21,"La Mam naongã ne M bugsgã yɩɩ wãn-wãna?"
  54,22,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd yolsa Alkʋrãanã tẽegr yĩnga, la tẽegd beeme bɩɩ?"
  54,23,"Ad a Ṯamuud rãmb kɩɩsa bugsgã."
  54,24,"Tɩ b yeele: ""ninsaal a yembr tõnd pʋgẽ la tõnd pʋgda? Ad tõnd wakat-kãngã d bee meneng la gãeemd pʋga""."
  54,25,"Rẽ yĩnga b sika tẽn-tʋʋmdã yẽ zug bal tõnd sʋka? A rag n yaa zĩrimbe-neda n yaa waoog-m-meng soaba""."
  54,26,"Beoogo b na bãng ãnd la zĩrimbe-ned n yaa waoog-m-meng soaba."
  54,27,"Tõnd n tʋms yʋgemdã, tɩ yaa zarbg ne-ba, bɩ f koll-ba la f maan sugri."
  54,28,"La f togs-b tɩ koomã yaa sẽn pʋɩ bãmb (ne yʋgemdã) sʋka, ned fãa wata a yũub (raare)."
  54,29,"Tɩ b bool b tũud-n-taagã, t'a rɩk (a sʋʋgã) n kõs (-a)."
  54,30,"La Mam naongã ne M bugsgã yɩɩ wãn-wãna?"
  54,31,"Tõnd tʋmsa b zug kaas-vuka, tɩ b lebg wala yãgr moodo."
  54,32,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd yolsa Alkʋrãanã tẽegr yĩnga, la tẽegd beeme bɩ?"
  54,33,"A Lʋʋt nebã kɩɩsa Bugsgã."
  54,34,"Tõnd tʋmsa b zug sob-fãeedga, sã n ka a Lʋʋṭ zakã rãmb bala, Tõnd tɩlg-b lame tõd-beoog wakato."
  54,35,"Yaa neema sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ, yaa woto bal la D rond sẽn pʋʋs-a barka."
  54,36,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, ad a bugs-b lame ne tõnd yõk-kεgengã tɩ b kɩɩs Bugsgã."
  54,37,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka b ro-a lame t'a bɑs bãmb ne ɑ sãambã, tɩ Tõnd yẽes b ninã, bɩ y lemb Mam namsgã la M Bugsgã."
  54,38,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, naong sẽn tabe n vẽeg-b yibeoogo."
  54,39,"Bɩ y lemb Mam naongã la M Bugsgã."
  54,40,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd yolsa Alkʋrãanã tẽegr yĩnga, la tẽegd beeme bɩ?"
  54,41,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka bugsgã waa a Fɩr-aoon zakã rãmbẽ."
  54,42,"B yagsa Tõnd yel-soalmã gilli, tɩ Tõnd yõk-b Wilb Naab sẽn yaa Tõogd yõkre."
  54,43,"Rẽ yĩnga yaa yãmb (Mak) kɩfr-dãmba! yãmb sõmblem n yɩɩd nin-kãeesã bɩ, bɩ yãmb tara põsg zĩig gaf rãmbã pʋgẽ?"
  54,44,"Bɩ b yetame: ""tõnd yaa zãma, d na tõoge""."
  54,45,"B na n sãeega zãma wã tɩ b gõd kuidsi."
  54,46,"Pa woto ye, Dũni wã yikr la b sεka, la Dũni wã yikr me n yɩɩd wẽng la toolem."
  54,47,"Ad nin-wẽnsã bee meneng pʋgẽ la bug-witim."
  54,48,"Raar ning b sẽn na n vuud-b bugmã pʋgẽ b nemsã zugu ""lemb-y Sakar sɩɩsgo""."
  54,49,"Ad Tõndo, bũmbã fãa D naan-a-la ne geelgo."
  54,50,"La Tõnd yεlã pa yɩ rẽnda vũka, wala nif kamsgo."
  54,51,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd halka yãmb buudu, la rẽ yĩnga tẽegd beeme bɩ?"
  54,52,"La bũmb fãa b sẽn tʋmã bee gaf rãmbẽ."
  54,53,"La sẽn paood fãa, la sẽn bedme, gʋlsame."
  54,54,"Ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee arzãn-rãmb pʋsẽ la ko-soodo."
  54,55,"Sɩd zĩndg zĩigẽ, Naab sẽn yaa tõog Soab nengẽ."
